    <activity xml:id="a-percent-change-real-world">
        <introduction>
            <p>
                Changes over time are often reported in terms of percents. 
            </p>
        </introduction>
        <task workspace="0.5in">
            <statement>
                <p>
                    According to the US Census Bureau<fn><url href="https://www.census.gov/quickfacts/fact/table/denvercountycolorado/POP010210" /></fn>, the population of Denver County was 600,158 people in 2010. Denver County's population increased 19.4% between 2010 and 2023. What was Denver County's population in 2023?
                </p>
            </statement>
        </task>
        <task workspace="0.5in">
            <statement>
                <p>
                    According to a local news report from August 2024<fn><url href="https://kdvr.com/news/local/rent-on-the-rise-report-shows-annual-increase-in-denver/" /></fn>, the median rent for a two-bedroom apartment in Denver was $2,470, a 1.6% increase from August 2023. What was the median rent for a two-bedroom apartment in Denver in August 2023?
                </p>
            </statement>
        </task>
    </activity>

